## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the latest developments in police practices related to juvenile delinquency. Additionally, the views expressed in the sources may reflect individual opinions rather than comprehensive research studies. Further empirical research could provide a more detailed understanding of the effectiveness of police involvement in delinquency prevention.